snippet.title: "BIONICLE: Legend of Mata Nui" Opening
snippet.description:
This is the opening cinematic from the unreleased video game "BIONICLE: Legend of Mata Nui". This video is provided for nonprofit research (history of BIONICLE) purposes. The video is a small fraction of a never-to-be-released video game from October of 2001 as part of a toy
line that is retiring this year. This video should have no negative impact on the potential market for the video game.

Thanks to "Deep Brick" for sharing the video.
